{"tid":1784513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[秘密搜查官系列]  逾30年首見 紐時：中國外交官刺探軍事機密遭美驅逐","createTime":"2019-12-15T17:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T00:39:59.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6f5c2ee874bef0be3556f248bb60323dc07e1826","tid":1784513,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"逾30年首見 紐時：中國外交官刺探軍事機密遭美驅逐<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201912150191.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201912150191.aspx&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=574fa771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201912150191.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓15日綜合外電報導）紐約時報報導，兩名中國駐美大使館官員在駕車前往維吉尼亞州一處敏感軍事基地後，今年秋天遭美國政府祕密驅逐。據信這是美國逾30年來首度驅逐疑涉情報活動的中國外交官。<br />\n<br />\n紐時援引6名知情人士說法報導，美方相信，此次遭驅逐的中國外交官中，至少其中一名是以外交人員身分為掩護從事情報工作。這兩名中國外交官9月偕妻子駕車前往維州一處敏感軍事基地，隨後並躲避軍方人員追捕，直到遭消防車擋住去路才停車。<br />\n<br />\n美中雙方皆未公開此一外交官驅逐案，但相關事件已讓總統川普領導的行政部門提高警覺，注意中國正擴大在美國境內的情報活動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國情報官員指出，中國目前在間諜活動方面對美國構成的威脅遠勝任何其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n美國官員指出，持外交人員護照的中國官員近幾個月越來越不忌諱在未事先知會的情況下，現身美國境內的研究或政府機構，而企圖潛入軍事基地不過是其中較引人注意的案例。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n1987年，美國曾驅逐兩名中國駐美大使館官員，理由同樣是他們疑似以外交人員身分掩護情報工作。今秋的驅逐事件據信是1987年以來首例。<br />\n<br />\n美國官員指出，這顯示美方已對中國的間諜活動採取更強硬立場。"},{"pid":"490db257099891a667511c765fea8ddc08285402","tid":1784513,"uid":251769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推，今日既行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnDkzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnDkzda.jpg&h=97bc3868&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PxUG26w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxUG26w.jpg&h=5e518208&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFiQbZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFiQbZT.jpg&h=b0320f4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6f09c41e96da4f223fb814595990cd23e9051c0","tid":1784513,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af23f38414d9650c0921ad010757b3736724007","tid":1784513,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"口交部呢"},{"pid":"9410c3d85ee90ecfbb45bde6a0d1f3db5796dfac","tid":1784513,"uid":9315,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:27:32.000Z","msg":"幾時驅逐埋加州D支那人  特別係學生?<br />\n真係有心查可能會發現全部老豆老母都係共產黨包括摺被軍高層黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那肯定唔係最近先開始滲透架啦  只望美帝真係強硬少少咪撚再以為同支那可以和平發展"},{"pid":"d9cd9b2abf918b37eb007aeeada61e05f5a13cf8","tid":1784513,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af23f38414d9650c0921ad010757b3736724007","tid":1784513,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"口交部呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:27:43.000Z","msg":"嚴正口交中"},{"pid":"663c3a76be7b7e4efe591e6d6da4cdbe88d059a0","tid":1784513,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc197617b8ae60ff3879b166575e2b947cc1c5d","tid":1784513,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:38:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔洗坐監"},{"pid":"4963a6613a13e6cd28b3ff58496cfe31447b6890","tid":1784513,"uid":19126,